- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is likely because the paper evaluates the performance of different machine learning algorithms for defect classification. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is likely because the paper discusses the use of soft computing techniques for solving a real-world problem in the aerospace industry.
